  2426	| `SPECKIT_CROSS_ENCODER` | `true` | boolean | `lib/search/search-flags.ts` | Enables cross-encoder reranking in Stage 3 of the 4-stage pipeline. When enabled, the reranker rescores candidates using a more expensive cross-attention model. Disabling falls back to vector-only ranking from fusion. |
  2427	| `SPECKIT_DASHBOARD_LIMIT` | `10000` | number | `lib/eval/reporting-dashboard.ts` | Maximum number of rows fetched for the reporting dashboard. Parsed as integer with NaN guard (`|| 10000`). Replaces a previously hardcoded limit of 1000. Added in Phase 018 (CR-P2-3). |
