  2429	| `SPECKIT_DEGREE_BOOST` | `true` | boolean | `lib/search/search-flags.ts` | Enables the degree-search channel in hybrid search. Re-ranks results by hub score via `computeDegreeScores()` with logarithmic normalization and a hard cap of 50. Base channel weight is 0.4. |
  2430	| `SPECKIT_DOCSCORE_AGGREGATION` | `true` | boolean | `lib/search/search-flags.ts` | Enables R1 MPAB (Multi-Parent Aggregated Bonus) chunk-to-memory score aggregation. Collapses chunk-level results back to parent memory documents using `sMax + 0.3 * sum(remaining) / sqrt(N)` to prevent multi-chunk dominance. |
